Question : 
How to remove the default value in a TEdit descendant ? 

Answer : 
Try this: 

constructor TDummyEdit.Create(AOwner: TComponent); 
begin 
  inherited; 
  ControlStyle:= ControlStyle - [csSetCaption]; 
end; 

  
  
  
  
